text: George F. Dannebrock (March 28, 1906 – July 27, 1989) was an American politician who served in the New York State Assembly from Erie's 6th district from 1945 to 1960. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Members of the New York State Assembly Category:New York (state) Republicans Category:20th-century American politicians
